description: The fund generally will invest at least 80% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the underlying index. The index is designed to measure the broad Argentina equity universe, while including a minimum number of constituents, as defined by MSCI, Inc. (the "index provider" or "MSCI"). The fund is non-diversified.
name: iShares MSCI Argentina and Global Exposure ETF
